title: Caitlyn Jenner Tells the Secrets of Her Life
description:
Caitlyn Jenner has seen some things. Three marriages, a ton of kids that she’s forgotten about almost entirely, an olympic gold medal, and the most successful reality TV show of all time. She’s also one of the most prominent trans women in the world and in her memoir, she writes about all these events and using her platform to help no one.
